<font face="arial" Size="-1" color="caffb0"><b>Target mob and taunt at least twice before breaking a mezzed mob.  Three times on longer fights (the longer the fight, the more the chanter has to mez them and the more they are mezzed the more they are pissed off at the chanter)</b><br></font>
